'''羰基氰化物间氯苯腙'''（'''CCCP'''）是一种[[氧化磷酸化|氧化磷酸化]]抑制剂。它是一种{{link-en|离子载体|ionophore}}。一般来说，CCCP导致细胞的逐渐损害以及生命体的死亡。<ref name="park97">
{{cite journal
|author=J.W. Park
|coauthors=S.Y. Lee, J.Y. Yang, H.W. Rho, B.H. Park, S.N. Lim, J.S. Kim, H.R. Kim
|year=1997
|title=Effect of carbonyl cyanide m-chlorophenylhydrazone (CCCP) on the dimerization of lipoprotein lipase.
|journal=Biochimica et Biophysica Acta
|volume=1344| issue=2 |pages=132–8
|pmid=9030190
}}</ref><ref name="brod99">
{{cite journal
|author=D. Gášková
|coauthors=B. Brodská, A. Holoubek, K. Sigler
|year=1999
|title=Factors and processes involved in membrane potential build-up in yeast: diS-C3(3) assay
|url=http://apps.isiknowledge.com/full_record.do?product=UA&search_mode=GeneralSearch&qid=1&SID=S1OH84h3mBDFNnOFaen&page=1&doc=1&colname=WOS
|journal=The International Journal of Biochemistry & Cell Biology
|volume=31 |issue=5 |pages=575–584
|doi=10.1016/S1357-2725(99)00002-3    
}}</ref> 它主要影响[[线粒体|线粒体]]中的[[蛋白质|蛋白质]]合成。<ref name="irku">{{cite journal|author=Y.M. Konstantinov|coauthor=I.V. Subota, A.S. Arziev|year=|title=Protein synthesis in mitochondria under different redox conditions|url=http://www.agron.missouri.edu/mnl/70/45konstantinov.html|journal=Preprint of the Irkutsk Institute of Plant Physiology and Biochemistry|volume=|issue=|pages=|doi=|access-date=2011-11-20|archive-date=2011-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110717183319/http://www.agron.missouri.edu/mnl/70/45konstantinov.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref> CCCP的作用机理是使电子载体在[[电子传递链|电子传递链]]的正常活动下形成的[[质子|质子]]浓度梯度[[解偶联蛋白|解偶联化]]。这种化学物质实质上以离子载体形式减少了[[ATP合酶|ATP合酶]]以最佳方式运行的能力。

